Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:54.78,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Close our eyes and recall the promises we shared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:01:02.24,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake off the falling darkness and keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:16.68,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I lost sight of the future I once had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:22.14,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I still see it from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:27.65,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,My uneasiness welled up over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:32.78,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow I cut through it and kept moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:43.99,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,The endless march of time announces a new beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:54.63,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Following my unchanging emotions, I open that sealed door!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:02:00.77,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,My awakening heart rushes forth, to draw the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:05.64,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how tough the path ahead is, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:12.40,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,a beautiful blue sky is waiting for me, so I'm not afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:18.74,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:16.44,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One day, perhaps the light of love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.94,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}which shines in your eyes will fulfill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.02,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}one dream of this scarred world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:30.87,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you would slake your desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:40.25,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there is no future but casting off your pride
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.47,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was a girl, I dreamed of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.85,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wielding something like unto ancient magic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:55.79,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be by your side as you smile, filled with the strength to smash even gods
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.46,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In my trembling hand, I grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:03.32,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the courage of a laurel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:07.12,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As my emotions waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:25.33,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my prayer awakens the light
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.21,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mami Tomoe.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A ninth-grader at Midakihara.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.25,0:00:25.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical girl contracted with Kyubey.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.94,0:00:41.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another weird dream...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.09,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Madoka!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.55,0:02:35.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were late getting home last night, Madoka.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.63,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An upperclasswoman invited me over.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.27,0:02:45.07,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to go on about your curfew, but you should at least poke your head in before dinner.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.43,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So people really can't see him...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.19,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a wonderful room!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I live alone, so don't worry about bothering anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not really prepared for guests.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.84,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami, these are great!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They taste amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.76,0:03:37.48,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Kyubey's chosen you, you're involved.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought an explanation was in order.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.31,0:03:43.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, whaddaya wanna hear?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.19,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she means the other way around, Sayaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Soul Gem.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.75,0:03:55.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a jewel born forth when a girl contracts with Kyubey.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.75,0:04:00.33,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of their mystic power, and proof that they're a magical girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Contracts?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.61,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fulfill any one of your wishes!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.71,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what! I'll make miracles happen!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.43,0:04:18.79,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabulous riches!? Immortality!? Maybe even a feast fit for an Emperor!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That last one is kind of...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.78,0:04:29.37,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, those who hold one of these jewels—a Soul Gem—has the duty to fight witches.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.62,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... What if?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.44,0:04:46.52,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were told that magic would make any of your wishes come true, what would you do?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.48,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd get rid of both the chief partners at my company.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.95,0:05:01.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The president's getting way too old, but he says he won't retire until he has a replacement.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take over?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.80,0:05:19.30,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get sales to go along with it, planning should fall in line. The only problem is old Baldy the beancounter...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, you look scary...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.52,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's a witch?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they different from magical girls?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.35,0:05:36.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If magical girls are born from wishes, then witches are born from curses.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.23,0:05:41.16,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If magical girls spread hope, then witches scatter despair.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Made all the more horrible in that normal humans can't see them.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unease and suspicion, consumption with rage and hatred.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.37,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sow the seeds of catastrophe through the world.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.37,0:05:59.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a few unexplained suicides and murders are caused by witches' curses.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.20,0:06:04.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their formless malevolence eats away at men from within.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're so dangerous, why doesn't anyone know about them?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.77,0:06:15.09,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches conceal themselves within a magical barrier, never to show themselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.09,0:06:19.09,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the labyrinth you two wandered into.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty dangerous in there.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.74,0:06:25.98,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people who get sucked in never make it out alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you fight against things that scary?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.00,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I risk my life.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't mind if you think it over carefully before deciding.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.73,0:06:40.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were chosen by Kyubey, you have the chance to make any of your wishes come true.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in return, you risk your life.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.82,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.74,0:06:54.43,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you come along on a witch hunt?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.73,0:06:59.82,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see what it means to fight witches for yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.82,0:07:07.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll help you decide carefully whether there's something you want so badly you'd risk your life for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.27,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Mornin.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.16,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.21,0:07:24.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who can see him, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.86,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! Let's just get going.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.71,0:07:36.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk just by thinking.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.51,0:07:40.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We already have that kind of magical power?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.35,0:07:44.91,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just passing messages.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, though. Nice and convenient!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.52,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels kinda weird...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.85,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you two?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.02,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep looking like you're about to say something.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.33,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.21,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.70,0:08:04.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you can understand each other just by gazing into each other's eyes already!?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you went that far in just one day!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.10,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two even do last night!?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.56,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot happened, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.56,0:08:20.19,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls can't do that!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's forbidden love!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.92,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your bag!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.86,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi's acting like you today, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.61,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean!?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.81,0:08:49.86,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you look pretty unconcerned about being at school.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.75,0:08:55.84,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that girl from yesterday just transferred into our class.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.30,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she trying to kill you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm safer at school. Mami's here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.55,0:09:06.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a ninth-grader. Isn't she pretty far away?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I can hear you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.83,0:09:13.15,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's within range of my telepathy!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.68,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.27,0:09:23.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm keeping an eye on you. I don't think she'd go after him in public anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.58,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.13,0:09:41.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that transfer student is a magical girl like you, Mami?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.51,0:09:45.96,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it. A strong one, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then isn't she an ally of justice devoted to hunting witches too?{o hi amelia}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.76,0:09:53.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd she attack Madoka, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.06,0:09:55.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was after me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.54,0:09:59.70,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wanted to stop a new magical girl from being born.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.77,0:10:05.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be fighting the same thing, so why not another ally?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.92,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.92,0:10:11.03,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, you'd be more competition.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.44,0:10:17.02,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating a witch has its own rewards.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.02,0:10:22.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So under the right circumstances, we end up clashing.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.91,0:10:28.56,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it caught her attention when Kyubey first called out to Madoka,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why she was after Madoka all day?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.04,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Madoka!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.04,0:10:45.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she tries anything, I'll smack her a good one!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got Mami backing us up too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.55,0:10:52.46,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm not sure how much good Sayaka will do, but I'm here for you. {gonna be pilloried for this~}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you don't know how much good I'll do!?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.30,0:11:04.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So so far you've studied referring to people and things in the active voice.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.55,0:11:13.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're going to work on the passive voice, where B is affected by A!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.66,0:11:18.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These sentences are formed by combining B and a past participle of a transitive verb.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, "kare ga atashi no koto ga suki" means "He likes me."
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Madoka.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.52,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought up a wish?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.09,0:11:43.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of figured everyone would have one, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of things I want and things I'd like to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.24,0:11:51.05,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get over the "risking my life" part.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything {\i1}that{\i0}  bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.90,0:11:59.20,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm surprised. Most girls go right for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're just ignorant.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.85,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ignorance is bliss.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.38,0:12:15.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like wishes you'd give your life for are that unusual.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.49,0:12:21.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess lots of people out there have them.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.13,0:12:29.87,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we can't think of any because of how lucky we are...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.96,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ignorance is truly a blessing.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why us?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.99,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't fair!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.99,0:12:47.46,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who would love a chance like this!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.70,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.88,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Picking up where you left off yesterday?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.02,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no such intention.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.32,0:13:16.56,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to finish him off before he met Madoka Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.15,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.11,0:13:25.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do? Will you become a magical girl too?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.33,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right to ask!?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.20,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what I said yesterday?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.02,0:13:39.32,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I won't warn you twice.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.84,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Homura!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wish for when you became a magical girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.36,0:14:14.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hitomi, we've got something to take care of.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another secret?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.54,0:14:24.85,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous! I just feel like a fifth wheel now!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.06,0:14:30.97,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get a coffee after school!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy today.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.08,0:14:48.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time for your first experience of what it's like to be a magical girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.17,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.61,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if this is enough, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.99,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what I brought!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figure it's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.77,0:15:04.71,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad you're prepared for that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring anything, Madoka?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.97,0:15:21.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should start with a design.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.03,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're certainly enthusiastic enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, you've got me beat.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trace of the magic the witch used yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tracking forms the basis of witch-hunting.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.39,0:15:50.05,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Soul Gem, we can follow the aura witches leave.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.79,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's less fantastic than I expected.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.91,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not lighting up at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.91,0:16:04.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I let her go yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her tracks have faded.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had gone straight after her...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I would've caught her.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.86,0:16:15.37,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But dealing with you two was more important.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.04,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.04,0:16:18.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were an ally of justice!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.47,0:16:26.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, that transfer student is a real pain in the butt!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.68,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's really that bad...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.53,0:16:50.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mami, do you have any idea where the witch might be hiding?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.13,0:16:55.09,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A witch's curse can have the most impact around crimes and accidents.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.09,0:17:00.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's best to check major roads and red-light districts where fights tend to break out.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.34,0:17:04.33,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, deserted areas suitable for suicide.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worst when they haunt hospitals.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.55,0:17:15.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They suck life force from those already weakened, with no one the wiser.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strong magical wave.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.89,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's close...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mami!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A witch's kiss...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. She's just fainted.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.30,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away today.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.99,0:18:32.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more for peace of mind than anything, but you should be able to protect yourself with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.00,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.03,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,St—stay away!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.53,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.03,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.70,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.18,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.86,0:19:24.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going! You're almost to the focus of the barrier!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.20,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. That's a witch.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.89,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.63,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight that?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.91,0:20:01.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.47,0:20:58.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to look lame in front of girls who're going to be my juniors!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was disappointing.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Erupt Finale!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.58,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She won!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.85,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Grief Seed.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The egg of a witch.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.31,0:21:58.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lucky, you'll find them on witches.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.35,0:22:01.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's perfectly safe in that form.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.66,0:22:04.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, it's precious for how useful it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.63,0:22:09.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Gem has dimmed since yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.06,0:22:12.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But using a Grief Seed...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:12.95,0:22:14.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.49,0:22:18.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It cleared up!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.11,0:22:19.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.35,0:22:22.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It restored the magical power I used.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:22.47,0:22:26.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reward for hunting witches I mentioned earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:32.14,0:22:34.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has one use left.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.79,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have it.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.62,0:22:41.18,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura Akemi.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.18,0:22:42.08,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.84,0:22:47.19,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you have something against sharing?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your prize.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:49.14,0:22:51.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to you alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's your answer.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.37,0:23:04.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really ticks me off!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.45,0:23:06.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could get along with her...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.59,0:23:09.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.81,0:23:18.07,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.66,0:23:24.09,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no? Why did I—
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.41,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I going to do that!?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You're okay now.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.94,0:23:32.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:33.22,0:23:36.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed, huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.37,0:23:45.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too hard for me to decide on a wish I want granted right away.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.78,0:23:51.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really admire Mami working so hard to help people.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.84,0:23:56.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become such a helpful person...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.74,0:24:00.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:01.10,0:24:03.00,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.40,0:24:10.82,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She puts on a cool air, but she's too shy and scared to talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:10.82,0:24:15.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting alone and crying isn't what a magical girl should be doing.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:16.77,0:24:18.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
